; hello.flld — Flommodore Linker Description (Phase 8 8.5)
;
; The code rule is first and uses AT: its value is the .flapp load
; address, and $04100 is the canonical one - the start of free RAM,
; where the BIOS autoboot scan looks (amendment 2.3 / E4).

ENTRY start              ; entry point symbol name

SECTION code AT $04100   ; place code at the start of free RAM
SECTION data AFTER code  ; data immediately after code
SECTION bss  AFTER data  ; zero-initialised space after that
